{"tid":924302,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港史】原來香港人幫英軍手打清朝?港人開埠初真的愛國反英?","createTime":"2018-12-02T04:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T11:43:39.000Z","uid":78029,"like":54,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"82e28c5bdf580530fb6e4fa3cbb8d0ee7607e531","tid":924302,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:04:24.000Z","msg":"大家好，又係小弟，小弟開咗個Youtube channel ，希望分享吓有趣小知識(心理學, 科學, 歷史, 甚至政治)<br />\n<br />\n今次講吓教科書唔會教的香港歷史, 例如未開埠前有香港人幫英軍補給, 香港人唔係大中華史觀講到咁愛國 <br />\n如有不足, 麻煩指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3VyGBBak9Qs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3VyGBBak9Qs&d=SjzH5d%2B%2FsKn5MNMwa28LvkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=2cabb2b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3VyGBBak9Qs</a><br />\n<br />\n上次講吓新學到的知識有幾快會被遺忘,  又會遺忘幾多, 同埋我地有咩方法去減少遺忘, 將學到的知識由短期記憶轉化成長期記憶<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gHNy4VD0nEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgHNy4VD0nEA&d=SjzH5d%2B%2FsKn5MNMwa28LvkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=dc5fb884\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gHNy4VD0nEA</a><br />\n<br />\n上上次講吓科學界點睇「世界上有無外星人? 如果有, 點解外星人無和我們接觸?」呢個問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3ob8lj7OM5Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3ob8lj7OM5Q&d=SjzH5d%2B%2FsKn5MNMwa28LvkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=36142b50\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3ob8lj7OM5Q</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集想講吓近年科學點睇「成年後腦袋係咪不再進步, 只會退化?」呢個問題, 從而介紹吓 我地可以點樣增加記憶力<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=21byiVTSZhI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D21byiVTSZhI&d=SjzH5d%2B%2FsKn5MNMwa28LvkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=d2650335\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=21byiVTSZhI</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集由大腦科學角度講吓靈魂出竅/離體經驗係咩一回事, 科學界有無方法重現靈魂出竅<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JhjpNvT-U4g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJhjpNvT-U4g&d=SjzH5d%2B%2FsKn5MNMwa28LvkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=07d6d8ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JhjpNvT-U4g</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集由大腦科學角度講吓一D因為腦部受傷而成為奇才的人, 從而睇下未來科技有無可能將我地由普通人突然變成奇才<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eCEv3hfdco8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeCEv3hfdco8&d=SjzH5d%2B%2FsKn5MNMwa28LvkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=3eb4b079\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eCEv3hfdco8</a><br />\n<br />\n第一集係由大腦科學, 心理學角度講吓愛情行為, 例如點解分手咁痛苦, 點解開始拍拖時會睇唔到對方缺點: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mgTq1gYCsZA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmgTq1gYCsZA&d=SjzH5d%2B%2FsKn5MNMwa28LvkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=6fa381ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mgTq1gYCsZA</a>"},{"pid":"77bca1608fca4376668526555d4121cdc52503b0","tid":924302,"uid":55533,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:09:37.000Z","msg":"廣州當年英軍打到黎大把人幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為班北佬阻住廣州人搵食<br />\n係班北佬先咁仆街保守有錢唔識搵"},{"pid":"f3a4692f923eadca05e15883ea2a9307ed9463a8","tid":924302,"uid":78029,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:15:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/de/%E9%98%BF%E7%BE%A4%E5%B8%B6%E8%B7%AF%E5%9C%96%281868%29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fd%2Fde%2F%25E9%2598%25BF%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E5%259C%2596%25281868%2529.png&h=d6f5bdc6&s={SIZE}\" />阿群帶路圖<br />\n<br />\n有一個傳說, 就係話香港英文Hong Kong 係源自於蜑家人口音「康港」<br />\n話說, 英軍初次登陸香港島時撞失路, 撞到個蜑家女性陳群, 由佢帶路, 行經淺水灣道、香島道、黃竹坑道、香港仔大道、石排灣道及薄扶林道至西營盤「群帶路」。<br />\n當時英軍問呢到邊到,阿群就話「康港」,所以就叫香港<br />\n當然呢個只係傳說, 但都反映當初香港係住咗一堆肯幫英軍的蜑家人"},{"pid":"30f9d539dad28ae1d340ae559413b5ff04523c49","tid":924302,"uid":60120,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:18:39.000Z","msg":"英軍來了我帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb77a6c01f4369a8b0040c534387b0e705b8b3cd","tid":924302,"uid":78029,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"77bca1608fca4376668526555d4121cdc52503b0","tid":924302,"uid":55533,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:09:37.000Z","msg":"廣州當年英軍打到黎大把人幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為班北佬阻住廣州人搵食<br />\n係班北佬先咁仆街保守有錢唔識搵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:27:55.000Z","msg":"係架, <br />\n當中好多本身就係水上人, 慣咗同外國人合作<br />\n不過廣州都好多人反英, 唔止廣州, 連英國本身唔要香港而想要的舟山都好反抗<br />\n但香港的居民基本上唔反抗"},{"pid":"3b318dfaea5c79fe0ac79a401cad78abea3f2f40","tid":924302,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:34:54.000Z","msg":"而家再嚟我都帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d7d3b3149e1229e53fab6442eb6b88d7e6ead67","tid":924302,"uid":78029,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"30f9d539dad28ae1d340ae559413b5ff04523c49","tid":924302,"uid":60120,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:18:39.000Z","msg":"英軍來了我帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以大中華史觀話咩自古以來, 血濃於水, 其實得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話咩壓迫剝削, 暗示到擁抱大中華就無壓迫剝削咁, <br />\n英統治係有唔公平, 剝削<br />\n但現實係係大中華底下, 歷朝歷代(包括而家)對港人剝削壓迫可能仲大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237d22dee3d27862a0969e07a9e6e69bef5f5b64","tid":924302,"uid":78029,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3b318dfaea5c79fe0ac79a401cad78abea3f2f40","tid":924302,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:34:54.000Z","msg":"而家再嚟我都帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T05:03:35.000Z","msg":"咁之後可能有條路變咗叫「Intrusion帶路」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03e7fe3f748ffc7fe02f96977e888599fb73770","tid":924302,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T05:28:41.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dae1cdb90b0a92fcebc12875c92a4ed3ea0fa78","tid":924302,"uid":55533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3d7d3b3149e1229e53fab6442eb6b88d7e6ead67","tid":924302,"uid":78029,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"30f9d539dad28ae1d340ae559413b5ff04523c49","tid":924302,"uid":60120,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:18:39.000Z","msg":"英軍來了我帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以大中華史觀話咩自古以來, 血濃於水, 其實得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話咩壓迫剝削, 暗示到擁抱大中華就無壓迫剝削咁, <br />\n英統治係有唔公平, 剝削<br />\n但現實係係大中華底下, 歷朝歷代(包括而家)對港人剝削壓迫可能仲大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T06:03:20.000Z","msg":"根本自古而來沿海人就好憎中央政府扮撚晒蟹<br />