d":"7c8543d90680dc33d32ef6d38fdfae205b94d8f1","tid":924302,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:17:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063f32cfec1a54b31c4c0d216566b3689d8c81e2","tid":924302,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:22:44.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢愛國反英<br />\n明明就係愛國反清"},{"pid":"4e0074da9022d649f1f775f997ebaca27b132239","tid":924302,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c1c801c93c113ea6ac989613b02f8c2a52087b0","tid":924302,"uid":181997,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"f3a4692f923eadca05e15883ea2a9307ed9463a8","tid":924302,"uid":78029,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:15:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/de/%E9%98%BF%E7%BE%A4%E5%B8%B6%E8%B7%AF%E5%9C%96%281868%29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fd%2Fde%2F%25E9%2598%25BF%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E5%259C%2596%25281868%2529.png&h=d6f5bdc6&s={SIZE}\" />阿群帶路圖<br />\n<br />\n有一個傳說, 就係話香港英文Hong Kong 係源自於蜑家人口音「康港」<br />\n話說, 英軍初次登陸香港島時撞失路, 撞到個蜑家女性陳群, 由佢帶路, 行經淺水灣道、香島道、黃竹坑道、香港仔大道、石排灣道及薄扶林道至西營盤「群帶路」。<br />\n當時英軍問呢到邊到,阿群就話「康港」,所以就叫香港<br />\n當然呢個只係傳說, 但都反映當初香港係住咗一堆肯幫英軍的蜑家人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T07:07:50.000Z","msg":"即係好似澳門個英文名Macau咁，當時澳門仲未有英文名，話說有一日個葡萄牙長官去到澳門一上到水就求其的個碼頭苦力種問澳門有冇英文名，但係個苦力唔睬佢一直行去啲貨度，咁個長官咪追上前問多個苦力一次，咁個苦力直頭望都唔望佢，個長官咪再好大聲咁用葡萄牙文問個苦力，最終個苦力終於答佢<br />\n苦力:&rdquo;<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">乜𨳊丫！！</span>&rdquo;<br />\n長官:Macau"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:23:28.000Z","msg":"葡萄牙個官講英文？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9756d9819e900c1993e7cc460fd058ff3d7aec5a","tid":924302,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8636900abd9d28af777baa108603d59697ea427","tid":924302,"uid":191926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T10:32:01.000Z","msg":"只可以講英治香港<br />\n<br />\n係支那幾千年內最好的境內政權<br />\n<br />\n就算係堆所謂盛世<br />\n平民都係賤過狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:25:11.000Z","msg":"支那境內？<br />\n請定義支那"},{"pid":"96ee07e0a1d828fbceb91ef19d3582247f64333a","tid":924302,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"063f32cfec1a54b31c4c0d216566b3689d8c81e2","tid":924302,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:22:44.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢愛國反英<br />\n明明就係愛國反清"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:32:41.000Z","msg":"巴打你誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人被英國統治係被逼, 佢地實際愛國反英呢點唔係我講, 係愛國史觀的歷史書/ 著作所講, 佢地目的其實係想做政治宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如共產黨拍紀錄片香港滄桑, 香港百年, 仲有書局買到既好大部分都係愛國史觀既著作<br />\n<br />\n我整段片就係想引用其他史料, 去講實際情況唔係咁簡化, 咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最起碼香港開埠前同開埠初時的香港居民(蜑家同福佬)唔係咁, 佢地無反英, 亦唔愛國(清)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82382fcd1eaaef98b7a3d5aacc3bb1744f49cced","tid":924302,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3d7d3b3149e1229e53fab6442eb6b88d7e6ead67","tid":924302,"uid":78029,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"30f9d539dad28ae1d340ae559413b5ff04523c49","tid":924302,"uid":60120,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:18:39.000Z","msg":"英軍來了我帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以大中華史觀話咩自古以來, 血濃於水, 其實得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話咩壓迫剝削, 暗示到擁抱大中華就無壓迫剝削咁, <br />\n英統治係有唔公平, 剝削<br />\n但現實係係大中華底下, 歷朝歷代(包括而家)對港人剝削壓迫可能仲大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:45:35.000Z","msg":"血濃於水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n含撚啦有著數就自己友，冇著數就割席<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要不是五十年前香港人救濟你們支那人？<br />\n<br />\n你們數十億支那蝗蟲早已餓死了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a72335cda51a5be6d22390a2a4660265f6dbea5","tid":924302,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96ee07e0a1d828fbceb91ef19d3582247f64333a","tid":924302,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"063f32cfec1a54b31c4c0d216566b3689d8c81e2","tid":924302,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:22:44.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢愛國反英<br />\n明明就係愛國反清"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:32:41.000Z","msg":"巴打你誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人被英國統治係被逼, 佢地實際愛國反英呢點唔係我講, 係愛國史觀的歷史書/ 著作所講, 佢地目的其實係想做政治宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如共產黨拍紀錄片香港滄桑, 香港百年, 仲有書局買到既好大部分都係愛國史觀既著作<br />\n<br />\n我整段片就係想引用其他史料, 去講實際情況唔係咁簡化, 咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最起碼香港開埠前同開埠初時的香港居民(蜑家同福佬)唔係咁, 佢地無反英, 亦唔愛國(清)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:46:12.000Z","msg":"我講緊愛國反清咪就係話我國係大英祖國囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc30af3552915e44185e36f926ff0f81a4fd783e","tid":924302,"uid":181997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e0074da9022d649f1f775f997ebaca27b132239","tid":924302,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c1c801c93c113ea6ac989613b02f8c2a52087b0","tid":924302,"uid":181997,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"f3a4692f923eadca05e15883ea2a9307ed9463a8","tid":924302,"uid":78029,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"repl